videos.title: Freedom Kids - Elijah 3 Years Old! recites Bible memory verses (Scripture)
videos.description:
Freedom Kids.  Free Christian resource for parents, teachers, churches and kids!
http://www.freedomkids.org/

Three year old Elijah reciting the Scriptures he has learned using the Freedom Kids program!  At the age of 3 Elijah had over 20 Scriptures memorized!!!  
Freedom Kids is a Biblically based learning program for children.   

Visit us at http://www.freedomkids.org/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pages/Freedom-Kids/305065042851434
